D/w Between StringBuffer and StringBuilder
  
    Both StringBuffer and StringBuilder are classes in Java
    
    StringBuilder is exactly same as StringBuffer (including  Methods and Constructor)
    
             StringBuffer                                       StringBuilder
  1. In StringBuffer every mthod is Synchronized       1. In StringBuilder every mthod is Non-Synchronized
  2. Thread-Safe                                       2. Thread-Not Safe
  3. Performane is low                                 3. Performane is high
  4. Introduced in 1.0 version                         4. Introduced in 1.5 version
